rozložení na stránce grid:
soubor ccs:
.reference-tlacitko {
    background: #70B73A;
    color: white;
    font-size: 1em;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: none;
    padding: 10px;
    border-radius: 25px;
    border: groove;
    box-shadow: 12px 12px 17px #1c2228;
}
.grid-container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 26fr auto auto;
  grid-template-rows: 16fr auto auto;
  gap: 10px;
  background-color: #2196F3;
  padding: 20px;
}
.grid-container > div {
  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  text-align: center;
  padding: 20px 0;
  font-size: 30px;
}
